      <title>加拿大在美国报复威胁下实施数字服务税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国警告称将采取贸易报复措施，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多领导的政府仍批准对大型外国科技公司征收数字服务税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-04/canada-enacts-digital-services-tax-despite-us-retaliation-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 02:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
